entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've destroyed the research data, keeping it out of Jabba's reach. You must now confront Dren and kill the mad man behind this atrocity.
entries.journal_entry_description: The information found in the White Thranta computers has been revealed as data collected from experimentation on sapient races. The data from the experiments must be destroyed for the safety of all.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Reimos wants you to go back into the White Thranta labs and destroy their medical research data. Let the dead from their callous research rest in peace.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Erase Data from the Medical Data Console
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Outstanding! The data has been destroyed. You have certainly earned your pay this time. Now all that is left is to take out the manager; Durr Roddack.
